`sparql
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT (SUBSTR(STR(?lang),32) AS ?wd) (COUNT(DISTINCT ?q) AS ?mcount)
WHERE {
?q (wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]*) wd:[entity:manuscript].
?q p:[property:collection] ?s. ?s ps:[property:collection] ?collection . MINUS {?s pq:[property:end time] []}.
MINUS { ?s ps:[property:collection] wd:[entity:Matenadaran] }
?q wdt:[property:language of work or name] ?lang
}
GROUP BY ?lang
ORDER BY DESC(?mcount)
LIMIT 10`

`sparql
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX psv: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?person ?personLabel ?dob ?dod (xsd:integer(?age_) as ?age)
where {
# We do a subquery here, because otherwise we'll get a timeout because of the labels
{
SELECT DISTINCT ?person ?dob ?dod ?age_
where {
?person wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:human]; # Get all humans
wdt:[property:occupation]/wdt:[property:subclass of]* wd:[entity:musician]; # That have a musician or a subclass thereof as their occupation
p:[property:date of birth] ?dob_st; # death of birth
p:[property:date of death] ?dod_st. # death of death
?dob_st psv:[property:date of birth] [ wikibase:timeValue ?dob; wikibase:timePrecision ?dob_prec ];
a wikibase:BestRank.
?dod_st psv:[property:date of death] [ wikibase:timeValue ?dod; wikibase:timePrecision ?dod_prec ];
a wikibase:BestRank.
# Only accept date precisions of a day or better, so it doesn't cause problems when we calculate age
FILTER(?dob_prec >= 11 && ?dod_prec >= 11)
# Time differences in Blazegraph are counted as days and is xsd:double
# We then calculate the age by dividing this by the orbital period of Earth
# This is a shortcut, but it is accurate enough for our purposes
bind((?dod - ?dob) / 365.2564 as ?age_)
# And filter by age
filter(?age_ >= 27.0 && ?age_ < 28.0)
}
#LIMIT 1000
}
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY desc(?dod) # Order by most recent`

`sparql
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?place ?placeLabel ?item ?itemLabel ?coord
WHERE
{
?item wdt:[property:named after] ?place .
?place wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coord .
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "fr" }
}`

`sparql
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?image WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:painting] .
?item wdt:[property:depicts]/wdt:[property:located in the administrative territorial entity] wd:[entity:Haarlem] .
?item wdt:[property:image] ?image .
BIND(MD5(CONCAT(str(?item),str(RAND()))) as ?random)
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en"}
} ORDER BY ?random
LIMIT 100`

`sparql
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?link (MIN(?image) AS ?img) ?qLabel (COUNT(DISTINCT ?sitelink) AS ?linkcount) WHERE {
?q (wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]*) wd:[entity:manuscript].
FILTER (?q != wd:[entity:Dead Sea scrolls]) # Exclude Dead Sea Scrolls: too broad
?sitelink schema:about ?q.
?q wdt:[property:image] ?image.
BIND(URI(CONCAT("http://example.org/test/manuscripts/index.php?q=manuscript/",SUBSTR(STR(?q),32))) AS ?link)
SERVICE wikibase:label {
bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en".
?q rdfs:label ?qLabel.
}
}
GROUP BY ?link ?qLabel
ORDER BY DESC(?linkcount)
LIMIT 100`

`sparql

{

?mouserOffice ps:[property:position held] wd:[entity:Chief Mouser to the Cabinet Office].

#?item wdt:[property:date of birth] ?startdate .

`sparql
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>

SELECT ?species ?speciesLabel ?sitelink
WHERE {
?species wdt:[property:parent taxon]* wd:[entity:mammal] # Sub-species of mammal
FILTER NOT EXISTS { [] wdt:[property:parent taxon] ?species } # Leaf nodes only
?sitelink schema:about ?species. # Page 'about' species: could be Wikipedia article or not
?species rdfs:label ?speciesLabel filter (lang(?speciesLabel) = "en")
}`

`sparql

SELECT DISTINCT ?identifier (SAMPLE(?identifierL) AS ?label) (count(*) AS ?count) WHERE {

`sparql
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?itemDescription (SAMPLE(?dob) AS ?dob) (SAMPLE(?countryForSport) AS ?countryForSport)
WHERE {
# occupation association football player
?item wdt:[property:occupation] wd:[entity:association football player] .
?item wdt:[property:date of birth] ?dob .
FILTER (DAY(?dob) = 1 && MONTH(?dob) = 1)
# not dead
MINUS { ?item wdt:[property:date of death] [] }
OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:[property:country for sport] ?countryForSport }
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en"}
} GROUP BY ?item ?itemLabel ?itemDescription

`sparql
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?item ?itemLabel ?itemDescription
(SAMPLE(?img) AS ?image)
(COUNT(DISTINCT ?film) AS ?count)
(GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT ?title; SEPARATOR = "; ") AS ?films)
(SAMPLE( ?film ) as ?sample_film)
WHERE
{
{ ?film wdt:[property:genre] wd:[entity:Christmas film] } UNION { ?film wdt:[property:set during recurring event] wd:[entity:Christmas and holiday season] ; wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:film] }
?film wdt:[property:cast member] ?item.
OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:[property:image] ?img }
OPTIONAL { ?film wdt:[property:title] ?title }
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
GROUP BY ?item ?itemLabel ?itemDescription
ORDER BY DESC (?count)
LIMIT 100`

`sparql
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?coords ?esgobLabel ?layer
where {
?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:parish] .
?item wdt:[property:GENUKI ID] ?id .
?item wdt:[property:coordinate location] ?coords .
OPTIONAL { ?item wdt:[property:diocese] ?esgob . }
VALUES ?gender { wd:[entity:male] wd:[entity:female] }
BIND (
IF(?esgob = wd:[entity:Diocese of St Asaph], "St Asaph",
IF(?esgob = wd:[entity:Diocese of St David's], "St Davids",
IF(?esgob = wd:[entity:Diocese of Bangor], "Bangor",
IF(?esgob = wd:[entity:Diocese of Llandaff], "Llandaf",
"")))) AS ?layer).
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY ?esgobLabel`

`sparql
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT (AVG($stardate) as $average_stardate)
WHERE
{
#star trek films
{?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:Star Trek film].}
UNION
{?startrek wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:Star Trek series]. #all star trek series
?item wdt:[property:part of the series] ?startrek.} #members of star trek series
?item wdt:[property:date of first performance] ?date. #get broadcast date (will create dupes if displayed)
?item p:[property:narrative location] [ pq:[property:time index] ?stardate ].
MINUS { ?item wdt:[property:instance of] wd:[entity:two-part episode]. } #exclude two parter entries
OPTIONAL {?item wdt:[property:duration] ?duration.} #allow no durations to examine furtherdown
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
}
ORDER BY DESC(?date)`

`sparql
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX schema: <http://schema.org/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>

SELECT ?itemLabel ?inv ?languageLabel ?sitelink WHERE {
?item wdt:[property:collection] wd:[entity:Ashmolean Museum]; wdt:[property:inventory number] ?inv # items in the Ashmolean and get their inventory number
FILTER (?item != wd:[entity:Oxyrhynchus Papyri]) . # exclude Oxyrhynchus Papyri
?sitelink schema:about ?item; # Wikimedia links (usually Wikipedia articles)
schema:inLanguage ?lang FILTER (?lang != 'en') FILTER (?lang != 'en-simple') . # exclude English language
?language wdt:[property:IETF language tag] ?lang # convert two-letter code to language item
SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "[AUTO_LANGUAGE],en". }
} ORDER BY ?inv`

`sparql
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel WHERE {
?item (wdt:[property:instance of]/wdt:[property:subclass of]*) wd:[entity:geographical feature].
?item wdt:[property:country] wd:[entity:United Kingdom].
?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel.
MINUS {
?item rdfs:label ?label2.
FILTER((LANG(?label2)) = "cy")
}
FILTER((LANG(?itemLabel)) = "en")
}
LIMIT 1000`

`sparql
